c%2Ft15%2Fs8811%2Fb%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"leverage existing Federal investments efficiently to advance Program goals and priorities established under paragraph (1).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
